Comment: 0,0:22:10.29,0:22:13.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{ED START}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.87,0:22:21.62,Default,ed,0,0,0,,There is one song I cannot ever forget
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.62,0:22:27.25,Default,ed,0,0,0,,Still, there's a face I'm willing to forget
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.25,0:22:30.21,Default,ed,0,0,0,,With her feelings messed up,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.21,0:22:33.09,Default,ed,0,0,0,,Alice got completely lost
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.09,0:22:38.28,Default,ed,0,0,0,,The midst of summer \NBrought her into one tricky love maze
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.60,0:22:45.19,Default,ed,0,0,0,,I want you to hug tightly\NAnd never let go of me,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.19,0:22:50.57,Default,ed,0,0,0,,One scared and timid tiny girl
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.57,0:22:57.45,Default,ed,0,0,0,,I quite remember our very first kiss \NAnd the beginning of all of this
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.03,0:23:03.87,Default,ed,0,0,0,,While birds were singing for us...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.94,0:23:13.06,Default,ed,0,0,0,,I'll take a car and take a lonely trip
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.06,0:23:18.26,Default,ed,0,0,0,,I know it'll bring me \NTo the seashore
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.26,0:23:21.31,Default,ed,0,0,0,,Where only the the sun,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.31,0:23:24.35,Default,ed,0,0,0,,Dazzlingly bright,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.35,0:23:29.88,Default,ed,0,0,0,,Could witness my long-awaited happiness
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.03,0:02:04.49,Default,,0,0,0,,7 to 5, 2 to 6, 0 to 6. Two sets to one.\NMatch won by Sekiguchi!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.87,0:02:10.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You can still participate in the second round.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.42,0:02:14.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Six days after the first defeat, \Nthe loser is allowed to play a repêchage match.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.09,0:02:32.10,Default,ep titile,0,0,0,,{\bord4\blur15\3c&HCEAC95&\t(0,1000,\bord0\blur0)\c&HFBFAF9&\fnGabriola\fs48\frz359.6\fscx169\fscy143\pos(358.714,342.858)}Episode 5 \N\N\N\NThere's no turning back now
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.20,0:02:42.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Father...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.69,0:02:47.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you afraid that not a single worthy fight will take place?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.16,0:02:52.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Makes sense. \NMidorikawa is out of competition due to a wrist injury.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.79,0:02:58.24,Default,,0,0,0,,And Oka has lost in the first round to a weaker player. Seems like your rivalry is now as weak as ever...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.24,0:03:01.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Still, I believe that Hiromi \Nwill make the best of the repêchage match.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.47,0:03:03.60,Default,,0,0,0,,So that's how it is...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.61,0:03:07.07,Default,,0,0,0,,She will definitely be doing her best till the end. \NLike Hiromi always does.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.07,0:03:09.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Hiromi, a phone call for you! It's Maki!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.14,0:03:12.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello, hello, Hiromi?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.63,0:03:17.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen, listen, you're not busy tomorrow, right? \NWhy don't we amuse ourselves?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.14,0:03:19.16,Default,,0,0,0,,You want to go watch the fireworks?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.16,0:03:23.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Right! We were invited to the third pier. \NI'm sure we'll have a wonderful view from there!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.52,0:03:28.39,Default,,0,0,0,,The real summer is already over. \NWe must make the best of its last warmth and party! Party!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.10,0:03:32.06,Default,,0,0,0,,You need some recreation now, \Nare you sure you don't wanna come?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.06,0:03:33.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll think about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.26,0:03:39.80,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the matter with you!?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.73,0:04:10.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey Oka! Will you at least start trying or what?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.71,0:04:14.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Continue hitting the baseline!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.40,0:04:20.17,Default,,0,0,0,,You came to the court to practice. \NWhat else is on your mind at such a moment?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.94,0:04:26.42,Default,,0,0,0,,If you are not planning to work, \Njust say so and get out of my sight!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.43,0:04:48.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Todo, now I know it for sure. \NTodo, you've lost your second game too.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.78,0:04:53.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And now you're all alone on a rainy court, \Nshedding unnoticeable, small, but bitter tears.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.37,0:04:55.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You're so far away...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.09,0:04:59.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Is going so far was worth it, Todo?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.39,0:05:04.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What hurts me the most is that I can't do anything to help you.\NIt's so devastating...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.22,0:05:08.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If only I could see your smile in front of me again, \Nhear your voice again...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.20,0:05:11.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The tortures my soul is suffering \Nwould've become less violent.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.54,0:05:16.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The more I'm trying to estrange from these thoughts, \Nthe more I'm losing my sense of reality.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.52,0:05:25.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Today, Coach Katsura scolded me especially hard for it. \NHe sent me home... But what home should I go to?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.52,0:05:28.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\fade(0,1000)}I don't have a place that I would call home now...{\i0}
Dialogue: 1,0:05:28.03,0:05:32.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\fade(1000,0)}I want to see you... I want to see you.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.01,0:05:33.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I want to see you!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.70,0:05:37.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}In his letters, Todo didn't utter a single word about how hard are the times he is having.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.33,0:05:40.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But I still feel, I must help him somehow...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.88,0:05:50.88,Default,,0,0,10,,{\an8\b0\fnVerdana}Japanese Tourist Agency \NTours in the USA
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.39,0:05:53.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Todo, I want to...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.89,0:06:01.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.16,0:06:03.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Did I make you wait?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.03,0:06:05.14,Default,,0,0,0,,You bet; I'm sitting here for like 15 minutes now!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.14,0:06:07.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's quickly get us some cotton candy!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.14,0:06:11.81,Default,,0,0,0,,So, are you feeling better now?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.81,0:06:12.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Kinda.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.60,0:06:15.57,Default,,0,0,0,,And on that last match,\Nsomething just went wrong, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.57,0:06:18.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't wait for the repêchage match. \NYou'll definitely win this one, Hiromi!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.81,0:06:23.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Hiromi, is something wrong with your cotton candy?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.94,0:06:38.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Maki...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.89,0:06:39.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I think...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.47,0:06:44.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I decided, Maki.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.24,0:06:48.03,Default,,0,0,0,,What was it? I didn't hear a thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.80,0:06:51.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I have now...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.59,0:06:53.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Decided! I'm going to America!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.33,0:06:59.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Hiromi...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.48,0:07:10.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to New York.\NI'm going to see Todo!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.98,0:07:27.17,Default,,0,0,0,,So that's what this all about...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.94,0:07:28.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.32,0:07:31.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Didn't see that coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.45,0:07:32.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.82,0:07:33.99,Default,,0,0,0,,You are such a fool.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.99,0:07:34.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.70,0:07:41.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Sometimes, I can't stand you, Hiromi.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.80,0:07:49.77,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you say? \NYou want to miss the repêchage match?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.77,0:07:53.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. And my practices \NI want to ask you to suspend for some time too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.36,0:07:54.26,Default,,0,0,0,,But why?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.25,0:07:59.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Oka, I understand why you feel humiliated \Nafter losing in the first round.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.01,0:08:03.68,Default,,0,0,0,,But are you hoping to detach from the shame this way? \NDetach both from the shame and Ochou?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.68,0:08:07.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I wish I wouldn't have to. \NBut nothing else is helping. I can't concentrate at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.68,0:08:09.28,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter how hard I try to...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.78,0:08:10.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What is the reason? What is the reason!?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.19,0:08:16.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Answer me then. Which thing do you consider \Nthe most precious in your life now?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.01,0:08:17.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Answer me, Oka!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.51,0:08:21.29,Default,,0,0,0,,It's tennis. Ever since I was 16, \NI decided to make it the meaning of my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.93,0:08:24.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Not when I was 11 nor 18 years old.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.98,0:08:28.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Nevertheless, the time for me \Nto be completely confused has come right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.46,0:08:34.46,Default,,0,0,0,,In such moments, \Ndo you ever wonder what Munakata would have said?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.97,0:08:38.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Luckily for you I'm not Munakata!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.96,0:08:43.71,Default,,0,0,0,,And for that very reason, \NI won't waste my time on someone who's not interested in it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.15,0:08:52.65,Default,,0,0,0,,You need a passport now, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.65,0:08:55.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Going to America is not such a big deal today.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.21,0:08:57.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, gotta pick a plane first.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.23,0:08:57.43,Default,sign,0,0,10,,{\an8\b0\fnVerdana}International Travel Agency
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.42,0:09:01.29,Default,,0,0,0,,If they offer you different cost options, just pick the cheapest one and don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.41,0:09:05.81,Default,,0,0,0,,After all, it's the money issue \Nthat is most worrisome for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.89,0:09:06.91,Default,sign,0,0,10,,{\an8\b0\fnVerdana}ATM \NCash withdrawal
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.02,0:09:13.92,Default,sign,0,0,10,,{\an8\b0\fnVerdana\fade(2000,0)}Payment details of the ¥61,000 bill
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.95,0:09:22.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Even though it's the minimal fare, \Nwill it be enough for at least 3 nights?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.98,0:09:30.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Maki...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.59,0:09:33.07,Default,,0,0,0,,We always help each other when one's in trouble, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.07,0:09:35.85,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the kind of occasion \NI was saving my part-time earnings for.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.85,0:09:38.36,Default,,0,0,0,,But you'll be flat broke then...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.36,0:09:42.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop saying such nonsense! \NYou really need to get there, don't you? The New York?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.85,0:09:43.61,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.61,0:09:47.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Fine, then! If you refuse, I'll have to go with you! \NIs that what you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.60,0:09:49.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't hesitate!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.33,0:09:52.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Maki, thank you...\NI am so sincerely grateful...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.02,0:09:59.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you feeling alright about this? \NYou will have to face serious matters soon! Cheer up!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.49,0:10:03.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm home!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.02,0:10:07.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome back. \NBy the way, Ms. Ryuzaki called you by phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.94,0:10:09.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Madame Butterfly?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.10,0:10:24.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry for calling you out at such an hour.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.16,0:10:26.54,Default,,0,0,0,,No... Nevermind.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.54,0:10:28.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you tell me just one thing about Oka?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.42,0:10:31.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I know nothing at all!\NNot a single thing, I swear!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.54,0:10:36.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Ms. Aikawa, please consider that ever since Nishi High \NI've been constantly looking at Oka.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.05,0:10:40.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Both like her senior and like her rival. \NBut most of all - like her friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.97,0:10:42.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.19,0:10:47.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I've heard it from my father.\NOka refused to participate in her repêchage match.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.95,0:10:50.17,Default,,0,0,0,,How come Oka gave up so easily this time?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.17,0:10:54.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I beg you, Ms. Aikawa. What made her step back? \NPlease let me know it too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.67,0:10:58.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know... Nothing... I can't...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.64,0:11:01.14,Default,,0,0,0,,So, it's all about Todo, after all?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.16,0:11:06.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.02,0:11:26.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hiromi...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.58,0:11:30.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You had to choose what is more important to you.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.63,0:11:32.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And your choice was Todo.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.52,0:11:37.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hiromi... Most of all I was afraid \Nthat something like this might happen.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.96,0:11:41.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}As a player, nothing frightens me more than the path you are currently on.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.63,0:11:44.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}After making the first step upon it, \Nthere's no turning back!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.70,0:11:45.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hiromi...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.66,0:11:47.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hiromi!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.96,0:12:11.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Madame Butterfly!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.35,0:12:16.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I am surprised.\NDo you also need to rest?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.63,0:12:21.47,Default,,0,0,0,,At this time, it's more likely to see you at Park Hill on a special court. Turns out even you do relax sometimes?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.47,0:12:24.37,Default,,0,0,0,,No, It's not that special. \NI'm just meeting with Oka.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.37,0:12:25.84,Default,,0,0,0,,With our Oka?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.38,0:12:28.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Say, would you mind if I go with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.83,0:12:30.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd be happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.29,0:12:41.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I assumed such matters \Nare not to be discussed by phone. Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.53,0:12:42.44,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.32,0:12:45.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I've met with Ms. Aikawa recently. \NI know everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.27,0:12:53.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Coffee, please. "America."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.90,0:12:56.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Your flight departures at 6 PM tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.17,0:12:57.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.36,0:13:09.52,Default,,0,0,0,,A repêchage match is still an option for you. \NYou have every chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.52,0:13:12.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Shouldn't you try every possible way \Nbefore finally giving up?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.89,0:13:15.37,Default,,0,0,0,,It's no use...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.92,0:13:17.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Hiromi, I beg you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.16,0:13:19.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You haven't tried yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.38,0:13:22.38,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just... No use for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.66,0:13:40.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, are you alright? Feeling dizzy?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.26,0:13:43.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm completely fine. Excuse me...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.22,0:13:44.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Be careful next time.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.32,0:13:50.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Oka...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.29,0:13:55.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Does Coach Katsura know already? \NAbout your New York trip and everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.13,0:13:57.88,Default,,0,0,0,,No... I didn't dare to tell him.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.88,0:14:02.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, he won't be very happy. \NThough, to tell you the truth, he won't be sad either.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.38,0:14:06.47,Default,,0,0,0,,However, it's better if you make him know yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.47,0:14:11.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't forget that there's a lot of people around you who adore you. I'm not the only one who is worried!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.06,0:14:12.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.10,0:14:15.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a little jealous...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.07,0:14:22.08,Default,,0,0,0,,If I were you, I would've been endlessly hesitating, never daring to do something that desperate.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.13,0:14:30.40,Default,,0,0,0,,We will always be happy to see you back. \NOn the court.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.59,0:14:40.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, Hiromi... \NI really didn't say a word to Madame Butterfly.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.67,0:14:43.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Forget it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.81,0:14:50.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Well then, if your tomorrow's plane is at 6 PM, \Nshould I pick you up around 3 PM?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.57,0:14:53.47,Default,,0,0,0,,No need. I want to do it on my own.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.68,0:14:58.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Tomorrow, I think I'd better go there alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.03,0:14:59.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Like that, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.26,0:15:01.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I got your point...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.02,0:15:04.73,Default,,0,0,0,,New York, here I am!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.73,0:15:08.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Promise me then, \Nthat when you're back, you'll be smiling!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.20,0:15:09.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.80,0:15:30.99,Default,,0,0,0,,When your family noticed, what did you tell them? You didn't tell them the whole truth, did you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.99,0:15:34.76,Default,,0,0,0,,My parents would've been outraged. \NAnd demanding to know where I'll stay.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.76,0:15:38.38,Default,,0,0,0,,If I were you, I'd go for something innocent. \NKamikochi Park, for example.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.38,0:15:41.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I decided to tell them it's Karuizawa. \NBe aware!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.15,0:15:46.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Hiromi, can I come in?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.78,0:15:47.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.48,0:15:53.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Here, this might come in handy. \NA fine treatment when your intestine is out of hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.04,0:15:58.82,Default,,0,0,0,,And don't drink raw water, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.82,0:16:02.03,Default,,0,0,0,,When you go to a new place, \Nyou also need to get used to the local water.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.92,0:16:04.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.06,0:16:08.05,Default,,0,0,0,,And try not to catch a cold out there. \NHave you already said your goodbyes to Maki?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.05,0:16:09.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.18,0:16:12.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.01,0:16:14.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.89,0:16:16.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.74,0:16:18.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Well then...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.72,0:16:38.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Oka! Jump in. I'll give you a ride.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.45,0:16:40.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Chiba...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.28,0:16:44.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on. \NThe airport is far enough, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.33,0:16:48.05,Default,,0,0,0,,But I... Excuse me...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.16,0:17:04.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Hiromi, are you gone already?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.21,0:17:12.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess, after all you are already gone...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.47,0:17:12.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Oh, my!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.48,0:17:15.03,Default,,0,0,0,,It's you, Maki!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.03,0:17:18.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Mother... Aryagh! \NI mean... It's you, mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.42,0:17:20.89,Default,,0,0,0,,You wanted to go to Karuizawa with Hiromi?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.98,0:18:03.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I'll leave you here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.20,0:18:06.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.15,0:18:09.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I've always been eager to see you play, \Nregardless of place.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.05,0:18:12.57,Default,,0,0,0,,And I truly hope to be seeing it in the future too.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.76,0:18:15.54,Default,,0,0,0,,See you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.02,0:18:29.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, flight 118.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.73,0:18:39.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A dream... I feel like this all is happening inside a dream that is about to end.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.21,0:18:44.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I might have betrayed some people, \Nbut this is just a dream, isn't it?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.70,0:18:46.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I so much want to see you...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.04,0:18:51.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Todo, I so much want to see you before I wake up!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.79,0:18:58.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Departing at 18:00 flight to New York \Nis now ready to take its passengers on board.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.80,0:19:01.76,Default,,0,0,0,,The seventh gate is waiting for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.14,0:19:18.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm listening.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.94,0:19:20.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm listening.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.66,0:19:24.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Forgive me...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.43,0:19:26.68,Default,,0,0,0,,What for?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.68,0:19:28.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I just...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.37,0:19:29.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.68,0:19:32.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Forgive me, Coach Katsura...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.68,0:19:35.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell me your whereabouts this instant! Oka!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.05,0:19:36.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, Coach...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.65,0:19:37.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are you!?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.13,0:19:39.96,Default,,0,0,0,,At Narita Airport.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.40,0:19:47.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.95,0:19:49.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you having enough cash on you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.69,0:19:55.01,Default,,0,0,0,,To get to New York and settle there, are you having enough cash on you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.82,0:19:56.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.84,0:19:59.98,Default,,0,0,0,,If so, do your best when you get there.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.03,0:20:04.48,Default,,0,0,0,,You big dummy!!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.10,0:20:54.10,Default,,0,0,0,,She's heading to New York?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.64,0:21:02.64,Default,,0,0,0,,So that's how it is... \NHer sudden departure looked strange to me from the beginning.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.11,0:21:12.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, Father, Mother, \NI cheated you by not telling everything initially.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.27,0:21:22.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Oka is... No, your daughter is... \NNot a simple-minded lady at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.16,0:21:27.70,Default,,0,0,0,,And Todo is, as well... \NNot a simple-minded young man at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.77,0:21:53.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Now... There's no turning back.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.32,0:23:36.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Aikawa Maki here.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.84,0:23:40.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Hiromi has finally arrived in New York.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.75,0:23:44.96,Default,,0,0,0,,But apparently, Todo left his apartment. \NHiromi is so unlucky...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.57,0:23:47.92,Default,,0,0,0,,However, a lucky event happens to her next.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.92,0:23:50.76,Default,,0,0,0,,She suddenly runs into Midorikawa Ranko.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.76,0:23:52.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Now everything is fine, Hiromi!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.43,0:23:56.18,Default,,0,0,0,,You're with Midorikawa now, \Nso you two will definitely find Todo!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.80,0:24:00.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Coming soon: \N"New York, the city where Todo is now."